Torchwood 41 Episodes 4 Seasons.
Torchwood was a Doctor Who television spin-off. Captain Jack Harkness, the 
former Time Agent and con man from the 51st century last seen travelling 
with the Doctor, ventures to early 21st century Cardiff. There, he becomes 
a member of Torchwood Institute, a renegade criminal investigation group 
founded by Queen Victoria to battle hostile extraterrestrial and 
supernatural threats.
